SEASONAL SPECIALITY
Prepared in Pan Am's own London kitchen,
the seasonal speciality today is Venison in Red Wine Sauce
garnished with button mushrooms and lardons.
Served with red currant jelly.
We would welcome your comments and suggestions regarding
our efforts to give you an interesting and exciting menu.
